3. No rate limiting on login or password reset
4. No CAPTCHA protection
5. Session expiry warning requires JavaScript enabled
6. No admin panel to manually unlock accounts

**Future Enhancements:**
1. Email service integration with templates
2. Admin dashboard for account management
3. Rate limiting middleware
4. Two-factor authentication (2FA)
5. Login history log for audit trail
6. Configurable lockout duration
7. IP-based blocking for repeated attacks
8. Password strength meter on client side

