### Dependencies

**No New Dependencies Added**

All features implemented using existing dependencies:
- bcrypt (password hashing)
- crypto (built-in Node.js module for tokens)
- express-session (session management)
- Bootstrap (UI components for modals)

**Considered but not added:**
- nodemailer (needed for production email integration)
- express-rate-limit (recommended for production)
- express-validator (current validation is sufficient)

